T02TD3496E:150a-1: mri tyu panytsa na s'i ta t'a r'a s'a dha nam /
T02TD3496E:150a-3: 'chi ba slu ba sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3496E:150a-4: 'phags ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3496E:150a-5: sgrol ma'i thugs kyi 'khor lo bsgom //
T02TD3496E:150a-6: ched du zla ba drug gis ni //
T02TD3496E:150a-7: dngos grub thams cad thob 'gyur zhing //
T02TD3496E:150a-8: 'chi ba'i skyon gyis mi gos so //
T02TD3496E:150a-9: ngag dbang phyug gis bstan mdzad pa'i //
T02TD3496E:150a-10: 'chi ba slu ba bsdus pa las //
T02TD3496E:150a-11: phyung nas sgrol ma dkar mo yi ;
T02TD3496E:150a-13: sde bzhi'i dang po aam yig bcas //
T02TD3496E:150a-15: pad dkar zla ba'i gdan bltas nas //
T02TD3496E:150a-16: mdun du gsum la skyabs 'gro brjod //
T02TD3496E:150a-17: rang bzhin sgro btags gzhom phyir du //
T02TD3496E:150a-18: skad cig stong nyid blta bar bya //
T02TD3496E:150a-19: de nas smon lam mthu yis ni //
T02TD3496E:150a-20: byang chub sems kyi yi ger gyur //
T02TD3496E:150a-21: chu skyes dkar po'i dbus gnas pa'i //
T02TD3496E:150a-22: zla ba'i gdan gyi steng du ni //
T02TD3496E:150a-23: rdo rje skyil mo krung gis bzhugs //
T02TD3496E:150a-24: mchog sbyin dang ni autpa la bsnams //
T02TD3496E:150a-25: ston ka'i zla ba lta bu'i 'od //
T02TD3496E:150a-26: zla ba'i steng du yang dag bzhugs //
T02TD3496E:150a-27: rgyun rnams thams cad yongs su rdzogs//
T02TD3496E:150a-28: bcu drug lo lon lus can ma //
T02TD3496E:150a-29: sangs rgyas kun dang de yi sras //
T02TD3496E:150a-31: 'phags ma sgrol ma snying gar bsgom //
T02TD3496E:150a-33: re'u mig brgyad la yi ge brgyad //
T02TD3496E:150a-34: mngon par yongs su bskor gyur te //
T02TD3496E:150a-35: aom h'a gsal byed dbus gnas pa //
T02TD3496E:150a-36: bsgrub bya'i ming ni lte bar bya //
T02TD3496E:150a-37: mkhas pas rtse gcig yid kyis ni //
T02TD3496E:150a-38: nges par brtan pos zla drug bsgom //
T02TD3496E:150a-39: yi ge bcu yi sngags 'di ni //
T02TD3496E:150a-40: mi skyo'i yid kyis bzlas par bya //
T02TD3496E:150a-41: aom gyi yi ge dang por sbyin //
T02TD3496E:150a-42: phyi nas t'a re rab tu sbyar //
T02TD3496E:150a-43: tutt'a re las tu re phyis //
T02TD3496E:150a-44: sv'a h'a mtha' ru las kun byed //
T02TD3496E:150a-45: tshangs dbang khyab 'jug nyi zla dang //
T02TD3496E:150a-46: drag po phyogs skyong 'dod lhas kyang //
T02TD3496E:150a-47: ba spu'i rtse mo'ang gcod mi nus //
T02TD3496E:150a-48: 'chi bdag las rgyal grol ba bzhin //
T02TD3496E:150a-49: skra dkar gnyer ma skal ngan dang //
T02TD3496E:150a-50: nad dang dbul sogs mdor bsdus na //
T02TD3496E:150a-51: seng ge la sogs 'jigs chen brgyad //
T02TD3496E:150b-0: sdug bsngal tshogs @150b rnams rab tu 'joms //
T02TD3496E:150b-1: bskul ba med par gos dang ni //
T02TD3496E:150b-2: khang bzangs rin chen la sogs 'thob //
T02TD3496E:150b-3: ral gri mig sman rkang mgyogs dang //
T02TD3496E:150b-4: bum pa bzang po la sogs 'grub //
T02TD3496E:150b-5: snyan ngag dang ni smra ba mkhas //
T02TD3496E:150b-6: blo rno shes rab dri ma med //
T02TD3496E:150b-7: gzhan yang 'dod pa'i dngos grub rnams //
T02TD3496E:150b-10: sgrol ma dkar mo sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD3496E:150b-11: byas pa'i dge ba gang de yis //
T02TD3496E:150b-12: 'gro rnams rang byung sgrol mar shog /'chi ba slu ba'i sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
